<p><b>What is ISO TS 22002-4?</b> Abstract. ISO/TS 22002‑4 specifies requirements for establishing, implementing and maintaining prerequisite programmes (PRPs) to assist in controlling food safety hazards in the manufacture of food packaging.</p>
