<p><b>What are the 3 ISO standards?</b> Three of the main ISO standards include the ISO 9001 for quality management, the ISO 14001 for environmental management, and the ISO 45001 for occupational health and safety management. ISO 9001 is focused on quality management and sets out the criteria for a quality management system.</p>